item.title: Commands
item.description: Mouse Commands Button Action Left-click Zoom in Left-click and drag Draw rectangle to zoom into. Shift-Left-click Recenter image on point clicked. Middle-click Flip to Julia set (or back to Mandelbrot). Right-click Zoom out. Control-Right-click Zoom out more quickly. Keyboard Shortcuts Key Action (arrow) Pan image in indicated direction.
